title: Notice board

properties.name: description
properties.value: A Notice board may refer to:

content:
A Notice board may refer to:

  • The Notice board found in Draynor Village that serves as the starting point for A Porcine of Interest.
  • The Notice board found in Fossil Island showing the player's progress on building the camp facilities.
  • The Noticeboard in Watson's house showing built and filled STASH units.
  • The Noticeboard in the Hallowed Sepulchre showing personal and global statistics for the activity.
  • The Shooting Star Noticeboard in the observatory showing where shooting stars have landed.
  • Notices, a piece of non-interactive scenery found outside of the general store in Varrock.

See also[edit | edit source]

  • Scoreboard
